# Product Rules

This repository implements two MVP products:
1. AI Export Website Kit Generator
2. AI Technical Proposal / PDF Report Generator

The system is a structured deliverable generator, not a generic chatbot.

Always preserve the shared pipeline:
Intake -> Knowledge Pack -> Template Rendering -> AI Generation -> Validation -> Export Package.

Do not add large SaaS features unless explicitly requested.

Generated output must mark assumptions, avoid fabricated facts, include required sections, be exportable, and pass harness validation.
